snippet.title: UNCHARTED 2: Among Thieves™ - Game of the Year Edition - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
UNCHARTED 2: Among Theives™ GAME OF THE YEAR EDITION has arrived! 

Download the announcement trailer today!




UNCHARTED 2: Among Thieves is a trademark of Sony Computer Entertainment America LLC. Created and Developed by Naughty Dog, Inc. (c) 2009 Sony
Computer Entertainment America LLC.

Use of this item is subject to the PlayStation(R)Network Terms of Service/User Agreement.  If you do not wish to accept these terms, do not use this item. Video output in HD requires cables and an HD compatible display, both sold separately. This video will play on displays ranging from standard definition to 1080p.  However, this video will output at a maximum resolution of 720p.
